bring it home and recycle it

00:24:20.180 --> 00:24:23.180 position:56%
or we'll say to the teacher at
school, do you have a recycling bin.

00:24:23.180 --> 00:24:24.730
Yes? Sound good?

00:24:24.730 --> 00:24:26.040
That's what I do when
I go to schools.

00:24:26.040 --> 00:24:29.200
They look at me like I'm
crazy, but I'm used to that.

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:31.500
So yeah.

00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:36.540
&gt;&gt; So how do you feel about
the number of water bottles

00:24:36.540 --> 00:24:38.510
